videos.headline: LaMareon James takes opening kickoff for the 98-yard TD
videos.description: LaMareon James take the opening kickoff 98 yards for the Old Dominion touchdown versus Tulsa.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (LaMareon James takes opening kickoff for the 98-yard TD) 2021/12/20 ESHEET

videos.headline: Davis Brin finds Josh Johnson for the 23-yard TD
videos.description: Davis Brin connects with Josh Johnson for the 23-yard touchdown as Tulsa takes a 14-7 lead over Old Dominion.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Davis Brin finds Josh Johnson for the 23-yard TD) 2021/12/20 ESHEET

videos.headline: LJ Wallace makes great one-handed INT for Tulsa
videos.description: LJ Wallace goes up and hauls in an interception with his left hand to give Tulsa the ball back.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (LJ Wallace makes great one-handed INT for Tulsa) 2021/12/20 ESHEET

videos.headline: Tulsa's fake punt fails miserably
videos.description: Tulsa punter tries to run for a first down on 4th and 16 and ends up getting tackled for a loss of a yard.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Tulsa's fake punt fails miserably) 2021/12/20 ESHEET

videos.headline: Old Dominion fumbles into end zone for touchback
videos.description: Old Dominion looks like they have a touchdown from Ali Jennings III, but Tulsa's Tyon Davis knocks it loose and through the end zone for a touchback, giving it back to the Golden Hurricane.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Old Dominion fumbles into end zone for touchback) 2021/12/20 ESHEET

videos.headline: Tulsa breaks game open with a play-action TD
videos.description: Tulsa quarterback Davis Brin perfectly fakes the handoff, then lobs it over to Ethan Hall for the 4-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Tulsa breaks game open with a play-action TD) 2021/12/20 ESHEET

videos.headline: Tulsa takes down Old Dominion to take home the Myrtle Beach Bowl
videos.description: Tulsa beats Old Dominion 30-17 to win the Myrtle Beach Bowl and finish the season 7-6.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Tulsa takes down Old Dominion to take home the Myrtle Beach Bowl) 2021/12/20 ESHEET SOTFULL
